Ujung Genteng.title: Ujung Genteng
Ujung Genteng.byline: Ujung Genteng is a fishing village and beach resort in the Bogor Raya region of Western Java, Indonesia.

Ujung Kulon National Park.title: Ujung Kulon National Park
Ujung Kulon National Park.byline: Ujung Kulon National Park is in the far southwest of the island of Java, in Banten province in Indonesia.
